title: Problem:
message:
Problem:
  - cloned version of ImapNotes2 did not sync with my account
  - the Notes-folder is in PUBLIC.Notes but the app did not work
  - I cannot add any folder at root level
  - javamail does not return 'INBOX' from the response '* NAMESPACE (("INBOX." ".")) NIL (("#shared." ".")("shared." "."))'

Solution:
  - added the ability to explicitely specify the imap folder to sync with
